<HL>
   Technology:
   Cray Research,
   Sun to Launch
   `Parallel' Project
   ----
   By Stephen Kreider Yoder
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
01/22/92
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B1
</SO>
<CO>
   CYR DEC SUNW
</CO>
<MS>
TECHNOLOGY (TEC)
</MS>
