   <PERSON>STEVEN MILUNOVICH</PERSON> is a stock analyst who follows the
computer industry for <ORGANIZATION>Salomon Brothers</ORGANIZATION>. In a Page One
article, his firm was incorrectly identified.
   (WSJ <DATE>Sept. 6, 1991</DATE>)
